 :schema-version "1.0"
 :scenario-title "Evidence while resolver at capacity — submit_evidence works when resolver has exhausted maxConcurrentDisputes"
 :scenario-author "@kilo-research"
 :scenario-id "s-dr-094-evidence-at-capacity"
 :scenario-purpose "Verify that evidence can still be submitted for a disputed escrow even when the assigned resolver is at capacity (current-active = max-concurrent). submit_evidence only checks escrow state (:disputed), not resolver capacity."
 :scenario-notes "Capacity set to 2 at t=1020. Two disputes raised at t=1060/1065 fill both slots (2/2). Evidence at t=1090 on wf0 succeeds because submit_evidence reads no capacity state. Resolution at t=1120 creates pending, settlement at t=1200 frees one slot. Resolution at t=1220 and settlement at t=1320 complete wf1 (past appeal deadline 1220+60=1280)."
 :provenance {:author-id "@kilo-research" :author "Kilo Research"}
